WEBVTT

00:00:01.566 --> 00:00:02.366
Loops

00:00:03.033 --> 00:00:07.933
In computer programming, loops help us 
with repetitive tasks that we need to run

00:00:07.933 --> 00:00:10.300
until a certain criteria is met.

00:00:10.533 --> 00:00:14.733
In Bash, the two most predominant loop 
commands are for and while. 

00:00:14.733 --> 00:00:16.266
We will examine both.

